\par 
\par As for my children, well, my daughter, she is 13 now: she was 12 at the outbreak.   I think she was away at boarding school and she didn\rquote t really didn\rquote 
t know what was going on at the start.  It was only when she got to hear that her friends were affected by it that she kept ringing me up - how are you doing dad, how are the animals doing, have you still got them.  My lad 
