\par }{\b\insrsid1328142 So how did events unfold from you first seeing the pyre at Heddon to your sheep being culled?
\par 
\par }{\insrsid1328142 You are right, that pyre was back in February I think and we just kept monitoring the whole situation, just kept listening to the news and watching it and thinking oh it will go away. 
\par 
\par It got worse and on March 24}{\super\insrsid1328142 th}{\insrsid1328142  was our wedding anniversary and we went out, with a few friends, down to an Italian restaurant in Hexham.   And we were with a farmer friend PB, who lives a mile down the road, who i
