\rquote t remember and at lunchtime the next day he got a phone call from his wife to say we have got foot and mouth.  And I thought bloody hell I just got this feeling that I had been out with }{\insrsid8726086 [him]}{\insrsid1328142  the night before, P
}{\insrsid8726086 B}{\insrsid1328142 \rquote s farm is a mile down the road and I thought this is it, we have got it, we will be culled. 
