re about to go through it.  
\par 
\par That was the end of April but the outbreaks in the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname PlaceName}}Eden{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname PlaceType}}Valley{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
